---
title: Serrano Wrapped Chicken in Sage Butter with broccolini and roast potatoes
description: Serrano ham (also known as jamón serrano) is a smoked Spanish meat with a strong flavour that it gets from the long curing process it goes through. Its gamey taste makes a great pairing for the cheese-stuffed chicken breast it's encasing in this recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R13_W16_IE_IESC14742-1_Main__4high-42211a09.jpg
